thread.title: Angela

author: Angela
title: Angela
text:
Anthony has managed my property over the past 8 years.
I have found him to be very knowledgeable, helpful and patient with my numerous questions!
He makes himself available and is quick to respond to queries and maintenance requests.
I have never had any issues with rental payments, which is no doubt due to the thorough tenant selection process. My property inspections are conducted regularly and copies of reports always provided to me.
Overall, Anthony and the team at Nelson Alexandera are professional and a pleasure to deal with.
